WEBVTT

01:30.940 --> 01:35.000
[Dream of Golden Years]

01:35.350 --> 01:35.920
Come on.

01:35.780 --> 01:39.430
[1998]

01:36.640 --> 01:37.300
In a moment,

01:37.590 --> 01:38.400
let's see who

01:38.680 --> 01:39.590
can climb up to that pavilion first,

01:39.590 --> 01:40.070
okay?

01:40.479 --> 01:41.070
Ready...

01:41.160 --> 01:41.690
Ready...

01:42.039 --> 01:43.000
Go!

01:44.150 --> 01:44.920
Slow down.

01:45.530 --> 01:46.280
Slow down. Be careful.

01:46.280 --> 01:47.539
Slow down. Be careful.

01:47.680 --> 01:49.229
I'm first! I'm first!

01:49.229 --> 01:50.400
Yeah, you came in first.

01:50.400 --> 01:50.870
I couldn't even catch up to you.

01:50.870 --> 01:52.000
I'm losing

01:52.920 --> 01:55.759
more than just the memories
of two versions of myself.

01:55.759 --> 01:56.820
I'm losing my life,

01:57.150 --> 01:58.150
my feelings,

01:59.310 --> 02:00.350
and the moments

02:00.480 --> 02:01.840
that made me who I am.

02:03.000 --> 02:04.000
Only with those

02:04.510 --> 02:06.560
did I truly exist as myself.

02:07.070 --> 02:07.840
Now,

02:08.030 --> 02:09.630
I can feel something

02:10.030 --> 02:11.290
slipping away from me.

02:11.800 --> 02:12.520
And I...

02:13.430 --> 02:14.710
Am fading away.

02:18.670 --> 02:21.460
[Episode 22]
[As I Fade Away]

02:25.680 --> 02:26.430
You're back.

02:26.960 --> 02:27.890
Are you alright?

02:28.910 --> 02:29.910
You know already?

02:30.430 --> 02:31.560
How is Zhou Cheng?

02:32.150 --> 02:33.190
He has some minor injuries

02:33.190 --> 02:35.560
and needs to stay in the hospital
for a few days.

02:35.560 --> 02:37.190
You haven't eaten yet, have you?

02:37.190 --> 02:38.850
I'll heat up some food for you.

02:45.240 --> 02:46.430
Silly kid.

02:47.190 --> 02:49.280
Don't shoulder everything alone.

02:50.079 --> 02:51.310
Laugh if you want to laugh,

02:51.310 --> 02:52.710
and cry if you want to cry.

02:52.870 --> 02:54.470
No one will laugh at you.

03:34.960 --> 03:35.680
If I hadn't insisted on

03:35.680 --> 03:36.590
digging into it,

03:36.590 --> 03:37.520
maybe they wouldn't have...

03:37.520 --> 03:38.180
Zhou Cheng.

03:39.030 --> 03:40.160
It's not your fault.

03:42.360 --> 03:43.030
Zhou Cheng.

03:43.750 --> 03:45.410
I believe it's not your fault.

03:46.840 --> 03:49.640
But I don't have that kind of confidence
in myself.

04:44.040 --> 04:44.560
Hello.

04:45.480 --> 04:45.750
Yes.

04:45.800 --> 04:47.870
We worked on the Haihua Hotel project.

04:47.870 --> 04:49.800
Okay, let me take down your number.

04:52.159 --> 04:52.600
Okay.

04:54.240 --> 04:54.720
Ms. Xia,

04:55.310 --> 04:56.510
3 companies have already approached us

04:56.510 --> 04:57.600
for collaboration.

04:57.600 --> 04:58.630
Then take down

04:58.630 --> 04:59.270
their numbers and info,

04:59.270 --> 05:00.120
and we'll schedule meetings
with them later.

05:00.120 --> 05:00.950
I'm going out for a bit now.

05:00.950 --> 05:02.000
We'll set a time tonight.

05:02.000 --> 05:02.390
Okay.

05:06.480 --> 05:08.410
Has Xiaolan always been like this?

05:08.680 --> 05:09.750
You mean busy?

05:10.510 --> 05:12.040
Ever since I met Ms. Xia,

05:12.390 --> 05:13.520
she's never stopped

05:13.630 --> 05:14.760
for a single moment.

05:16.160 --> 05:18.040
If you hadn't told me,

05:18.680 --> 05:20.360
I wouldn't have been able to tell

05:20.360 --> 05:21.920
from her face at all

05:22.120 --> 05:24.380
that her boyfriend just had an accident.

05:24.760 --> 05:26.220
That's just how Ms. Xia is.

05:26.270 --> 05:27.430
She never lets her personal emotions

05:27.430 --> 05:28.430
affect her work.

05:29.160 --> 05:30.510
Last time she got injured,

05:30.510 --> 05:32.170
it didn't slow her down at all.

05:33.680 --> 05:35.340
Brittle sticks break easily.

05:36.830 --> 05:37.240
Look, you two

05:37.240 --> 05:38.240
grew up together.

05:38.390 --> 05:39.270
Why didn't you

05:39.270 --> 05:40.120
protect her properly?

05:40.120 --> 05:40.750
Auntie, Auntie.

05:40.750 --> 05:41.750
Please calm down.

05:41.920 --> 05:42.950
Zhou Cheng really did

05:42.950 --> 05:44.140
want to pull Jiang Yan out at that moment,

05:44.140 --> 05:45.400
but before he could...

05:49.630 --> 05:50.159
Auntie.

05:50.800 --> 05:51.390
Uncle.

05:52.390 --> 05:53.360
Regarding what happened to Jiang Yan...

05:53.360 --> 05:53.920
Regarding what happened to Jiang Yan,

05:53.920 --> 05:55.920
you must take full responsibility.

05:58.360 --> 05:58.920
Sure.

05:59.270 --> 06:00.430
I'll take responsibility too.

06:00.430 --> 06:01.120
I also grew up

06:01.120 --> 06:01.980
with Jiang Yan.

06:02.240 --> 06:03.680
I'll definitely take good care of her.

06:03.680 --> 06:04.120
Wei.

06:04.120 --> 06:05.060
Why are you interrupting?

06:05.060 --> 06:06.710
Is this any of your business?

06:06.870 --> 06:07.950
How is it not my business?

06:07.950 --> 06:09.000
Of course it is.

06:09.070 --> 06:09.600
Auntie, I think

06:09.600 --> 06:10.510
what you said is absolutely right.

06:10.510 --> 06:12.240
Jiang Yan works in Shengcheng,

06:12.360 --> 06:13.480
and we grew up together.

06:13.480 --> 06:14.000
It's only right that Cheng and I

06:14.000 --> 06:15.200
take good care of her.

06:18.160 --> 06:18.870
Who are you?

06:20.960 --> 06:21.820
Hello, Auntie.

06:22.240 --> 06:23.900
I'm Zhou Cheng's girlfriend.

06:34.159 --> 06:34.620
Xiao...

06:44.240 --> 06:44.600
Here.

06:50.950 --> 06:51.480
Xiaolan.

06:53.120 --> 06:53.950
That was

06:54.480 --> 06:55.610
Jiang Yan's mother.

06:56.800 --> 06:58.530
Her daughter is badly injured,

06:58.800 --> 07:00.860
so it's understandable she's upset.

07:01.120 --> 07:02.380
How's Jiang Yan doing?

07:03.070 --> 07:05.190
The doctor said she's ready for surgery,

07:05.190 --> 07:07.790
but they don't seem to
have made a decision yet.

07:07.830 --> 07:08.490
Xiaolan...

07:08.600 --> 07:09.360
Eat first.

07:09.520 --> 07:10.920
The food is getting cold.

07:26.190 --> 07:26.630
Hello?

07:27.680 --> 07:29.720
Du Zhaohui, what do you want now?

07:39.000 --> 07:39.800
I'm very busy.

07:39.950 --> 07:42.000
If you're going to talk nonsense,
I'll leave right away.

07:42.000 --> 07:43.630
Alright, I'll get straight to the point.

07:43.630 --> 07:45.500
I've got 20 million Hong Kong dollars.

07:45.500 --> 07:46.240
I want to make as much money

07:46.240 --> 07:47.040
as possible in a year.

07:47.040 --> 07:47.950
What should I do?

07:47.950 --> 07:49.000
Why are you asking me?

07:49.000 --> 07:50.159
Because among the people I know,

07:50.159 --> 07:51.560
you're the best at making money.

07:51.560 --> 07:52.600
You're also the least likely

07:52.600 --> 07:53.330
to be bribed,

07:53.800 --> 07:54.560
and the least likely

07:54.560 --> 07:55.610
to be set up as

07:55.680 --> 07:56.720
an undercover agent.

07:56.720 --> 07:57.390
Du Zhaohui.

07:57.720 --> 07:58.800
Even if I knew

07:58.800 --> 08:00.070
how to make more money,

08:00.270 --> 08:01.470
why should I tell you?

08:03.240 --> 08:04.600
I'll pay you.

08:05.150 --> 08:06.420
If I do as you say

08:06.480 --> 08:07.480
and make a profit,

08:07.560 --> 08:08.450
I'll only take back the principal,

08:08.450 --> 08:09.800
and you can take all the profit.

08:09.800 --> 08:10.600
I just need to run it through

08:10.600 --> 08:11.330
my accounts.

08:13.680 --> 08:16.070
Mr. Du, you're certainly generous.

08:18.800 --> 08:20.260
What are you really after?

08:20.510 --> 08:21.560
Twenty million Hong Kong dollars

08:21.560 --> 08:23.480
would earn interest
even just sitting in a bank.

08:23.480 --> 08:24.510
Your Du family has so many

08:24.510 --> 08:26.000
passive income businesses.

08:26.000 --> 08:27.530
Why make it so complicated?

08:30.190 --> 08:31.000
Could this have anything to do

08:31.000 --> 08:33.000
you fighting for the family assets?

08:34.909 --> 08:35.960
You're truly impressive.

08:35.960 --> 08:37.360
Your analysis was right.

08:37.510 --> 08:38.440
Old Man said

08:38.750 --> 08:40.909
whoever can make the most money
with 20 million

08:40.909 --> 08:41.360
gets 5%

08:41.360 --> 08:43.000
of the group's shares.

08:43.789 --> 08:44.240
No.

08:44.960 --> 08:47.020
You're still not telling the whole truth.

08:47.020 --> 08:48.290
Whoever gets that 5% of

08:48.320 --> 08:49.660
Chengrong Group's shares

08:49.660 --> 08:51.790
will be ahead of
the rest of the Du family.

08:51.790 --> 08:52.550
This isn't just

08:52.550 --> 08:54.210
a battle over 5% of the shares—

08:54.750 --> 08:55.840
it's a fight for

08:55.840 --> 08:57.770
the heir of the Du family, isn't it?

08:57.790 --> 08:59.390
Yes, yes, yes. You're right.

09:00.200 --> 09:01.390
But 5%

09:02.030 --> 09:03.630
is not a small amount either.

09:03.870 --> 09:04.670
But of course,

09:04.810 --> 09:05.720
the most important thing is

09:05.720 --> 09:07.120
earning Old Man's favor.

09:08.150 --> 09:09.000
I promise you,

09:09.390 --> 09:09.960
if the Du family

09:09.960 --> 09:11.560
ends up under my management,

09:11.600 --> 09:12.120
I'll definitely

09:12.120 --> 09:13.360
shut down

09:13.480 --> 09:15.000
all the smuggling businesses.

09:15.000 --> 09:15.960
That Jerk Zh...

09:16.910 --> 09:18.320
That boyfriend of yours—

09:18.630 --> 09:19.670
isn't he investigating

09:19.670 --> 09:20.800
the smuggling case?

09:21.200 --> 09:22.240
I can give him

09:22.240 --> 09:23.440
all the information.

09:24.550 --> 09:25.750
The Du family's money

09:25.990 --> 09:27.520
is essentially your money.

09:28.150 --> 09:30.530
How could you be willing
to shut down the smuggling business?

09:30.530 --> 09:31.600
Only the money that goes into my pocket

09:31.600 --> 09:32.560
is truly mine.

09:32.600 --> 09:34.510
That money belongs to the Du family—

09:34.510 --> 09:36.240
and the Du family isn't just me.

09:36.510 --> 09:37.390
I've thought about it.

09:37.390 --> 09:38.520
Times have changed.

09:38.550 --> 09:39.210
From now on,

09:39.240 --> 09:40.970
I only want to make clean money.

09:42.000 --> 09:42.870
I swear

09:43.120 --> 09:45.050
I'll only do legitimate business.

09:46.670 --> 09:48.390
Didn't Chairman Du
propose this competition

09:48.390 --> 09:49.320
just to test

09:49.320 --> 09:51.670
you and your younger brother's abilities?

09:51.670 --> 09:53.130
Doesn't asking me for help

09:53.200 --> 09:54.260
count as cheating?

09:54.940 --> 09:55.990
Old Man only said

09:56.020 --> 09:57.750
we couldn't use the family's resources.

09:57.750 --> 09:59.360
I don't believe that brat

09:59.480 --> 10:00.810
won't use outside help.

10:01.030 --> 10:01.550
Well,

10:01.790 --> 10:03.630
you're not part of the family resources.

10:03.630 --> 10:04.440
What do you say?

10:04.440 --> 10:06.120
I'll give you some time to think about it.

10:06.120 --> 10:07.320
Besides the payment,

10:07.440 --> 10:08.440
I've got something else

10:08.440 --> 10:09.170
to offer you.

10:10.960 --> 10:11.560
What is it?

10:12.910 --> 10:13.720
In a year,

10:14.270 --> 10:15.360
I'll hand Xia Ziyu

10:15.670 --> 10:17.200
over to you. How about that?

10:18.030 --> 10:18.790
Xia Ziyu?

10:20.150 --> 10:21.950
Old Man's new girlfriend, Vivi—

10:22.320 --> 10:23.550
she's also your cousin,

10:23.550 --> 10:24.810
Xia Ziyu.

10:34.550 --> 10:36.510
There's a ship to Gangdao
the day after tomorrow.

10:36.510 --> 10:37.440
If you want to go,

10:37.550 --> 10:38.680
get the money ready.

10:49.070 --> 10:51.320
You have no ID and can't speak Cantonese.

10:51.320 --> 10:51.670
Go away.

10:51.670 --> 10:52.440
I can wash vegetables and dishes.

10:52.440 --> 10:52.960
I can do anything.

10:52.960 --> 10:53.910
Go away. Go away.

10:53.910 --> 10:55.110
We're not hiring you.

10:58.220 --> 10:59.070
Look at

10:59.750 --> 11:00.360
that girl.

11:02.360 --> 11:04.290
Let's ask her if she's interested.

11:06.700 --> 11:07.510
Hey, beauty.

11:09.480 --> 11:10.360
Since you can't speak Cantonese,

11:10.360 --> 11:12.020
it's really hard to find a job.

11:12.200 --> 11:13.870
I can introduce a job to you.

11:17.870 --> 11:20.440
Everyone's like this
when they first come here.

11:20.440 --> 11:22.840
Let's see how many more days
you can starve.

11:24.510 --> 11:26.170
Why pretend to be so innocent?

11:26.670 --> 11:27.530
Give her a couple of days—

11:27.530 --> 11:28.440
once she thinks it through,

11:28.440 --> 11:29.700
she'll come back to us.

11:38.060 --> 11:39.650
Darn northern girl,

11:39.790 --> 11:40.840
cheating me of my money!

11:40.840 --> 11:41.500
Pay me back!

11:41.840 --> 11:42.790
You scumbag.

11:48.120 --> 11:49.000
Tired of living?

11:49.000 --> 11:49.630
What if you'd bumped into

11:49.630 --> 11:50.240
our Young Master?

11:50.240 --> 11:51.340
Do you have a death wish?

11:51.340 --> 11:52.200
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

11:52.200 --> 11:53.320
I didn't mean to.

11:53.960 --> 11:55.550
P-Please spare me.

13:04.720 --> 13:06.080
Mr. Du, that story

13:06.270 --> 13:08.200
is really full of twists and turns.

13:08.200 --> 13:09.120
It's fascinating.

13:09.120 --> 13:09.720
Is it?

13:10.150 --> 13:11.630
Stories like this happen every day

13:11.630 --> 13:12.870
in Gangdao.

13:14.270 --> 13:16.200
But since she had plastic surgery,

13:16.320 --> 13:16.960
how did you know

13:16.960 --> 13:17.890
she was Xia Ziyu?

13:18.470 --> 13:20.470
Old Man is suspicious and paranoid.

13:20.670 --> 13:21.910
Of course he'd investigate

13:21.910 --> 13:23.770
everyone by his side thoroughly.

13:24.440 --> 13:25.500
So, what do you say?

13:25.720 --> 13:26.630
Think it over.

13:27.720 --> 13:28.630
If you help me,

13:28.910 --> 13:30.840
I'll hand Xia Ziyu over to you.

13:31.840 --> 13:32.320
Also,

13:32.320 --> 13:33.870
there's no need to worry about Old Man.

13:33.870 --> 13:35.360
He has so many women around him.

13:35.360 --> 13:36.360
Once Vivi's gone,

13:37.360 --> 13:38.240
surely some other woman

13:38.240 --> 13:39.370
will take her place.

13:40.000 --> 13:41.120
Actually, I'm not interested

13:41.120 --> 13:41.780
in Xia Ziyu.

13:42.630 --> 13:43.600
But

13:43.750 --> 13:44.880
I know she caused you

13:45.070 --> 13:46.160
a lot of trouble.

13:47.060 --> 13:48.440
Regarding that trouble,

13:48.440 --> 13:49.150
I've already made her

13:49.150 --> 13:50.360
pay double—

13:50.360 --> 13:51.820
she's already a fugitive.

13:51.960 --> 13:52.690
Besides,

13:53.070 --> 13:54.480
what use is it to hand Vivi over to me?

13:54.480 --> 13:56.750
The one who belongs in prison is Xia Ziyu.

13:57.480 --> 13:59.120
It's just a matter of
changing her identity.

13:59.120 --> 14:00.910
Although it's a bit troublesome,

14:00.910 --> 14:02.240
it's not impossible.

14:02.840 --> 14:04.960
If the reward isn't enough,

14:05.360 --> 14:06.600
feel free to speak up about

14:06.600 --> 14:08.000
any other ideas you have.

14:13.630 --> 14:14.890
I've thought about it.

14:15.240 --> 14:16.030
It's better

14:16.320 --> 14:18.510
not to work with gangsters.

14:19.080 --> 14:20.550
Mr. Du, you kidnap people

14:20.550 --> 14:22.200
and throw them into the sea
whenever you feel like it.

14:22.200 --> 14:23.390
It really scares me.

14:24.840 --> 14:26.080
I'm so sincere about discussing

14:26.080 --> 14:27.600
a multi-million deal with you,

14:27.600 --> 14:29.060
yet you call me a gangster?

14:29.200 --> 14:31.270
Kidnapping and throwing people
into the sea?

14:31.270 --> 14:32.730
When have I ever done that?

14:33.080 --> 14:33.960
After all,

14:34.120 --> 14:35.240
I'm easily worth

14:35.240 --> 14:36.750
hundreds of millions, okay?

14:36.750 --> 14:38.550
I have so much to do every day.

14:39.480 --> 14:41.680
How would I have time for such bad deeds?

14:41.870 --> 14:42.200
Fine.

14:42.440 --> 14:43.640
Let me think about it.

14:43.960 --> 14:45.240
But even if I agree,

14:45.390 --> 14:47.320
the consulting fee won't be cheap.

14:49.560 --> 14:51.620
You're not leaving already, are you?

14:53.390 --> 14:53.960
Mr. Du.

14:54.910 --> 14:55.770
Are you willing

14:55.960 --> 14:57.420
to sell your house and car?

14:59.670 --> 15:01.120
Vivi is Xia Ziyu?

15:01.360 --> 15:02.480
She had plastic surgery

15:02.480 --> 15:03.680
and changed her name.

15:04.320 --> 15:05.920
Even though I told Du Zhaohui

15:06.030 --> 15:07.560
I wasn't interested in her,

15:08.150 --> 15:10.150
she's done so many terrible things—

15:10.150 --> 15:10.750
I don't want her

15:10.750 --> 15:12.550
to escape the law's punishment.

15:12.600 --> 15:13.750
If she keeps staying in Gangdao

15:13.750 --> 15:14.600
and doesn't come back,

15:14.600 --> 15:15.200
is there really

15:15.200 --> 15:16.660
nothing we can do about it?

15:17.560 --> 15:18.150
If she keeps staying

15:18.150 --> 15:19.300
in Gangdao,

15:19.630 --> 15:21.270
it's indeed quite troublesome.

15:21.270 --> 15:22.600
To bring her to justice,

15:22.960 --> 15:24.360
she must come back first.

15:24.440 --> 15:25.240
And secondly,

15:25.720 --> 15:27.320
we must prove she is Xia Ziyu.

15:27.830 --> 15:29.710
Besides her face and name,

15:30.590 --> 15:32.190
are there other ways

15:32.470 --> 15:34.200
to prove her true identity?

15:35.300 --> 15:36.180
For example,

15:36.480 --> 15:37.340
fingerprints,

15:37.750 --> 15:38.360
hair,

15:38.910 --> 15:40.110
or blood comparison?

15:41.750 --> 15:42.910
You mean that

15:43.430 --> 15:45.150
DNA identification technology?

15:45.150 --> 15:45.550
Yes.

15:45.910 --> 15:47.040
Is it available now?

15:47.320 --> 15:48.550
I heard it is.

15:48.990 --> 15:50.790
I'll ask my contacts
at the Public Security Bureau

15:50.790 --> 15:51.920
to ask around later.

15:52.600 --> 15:53.000
Okay.

15:57.270 --> 15:57.840
Xiaolan,

15:59.440 --> 16:00.900
stay away from Du Zhaohui.

16:01.870 --> 16:04.030
Jiang Yan has been keeping an eye
on the Du family.

16:04.030 --> 16:06.320
The Du family didn't just get rich
from smuggling.

16:06.320 --> 16:07.080
Even now,

16:07.080 --> 16:09.150
they still haven't completely
severed ties.

16:09.150 --> 16:09.960
I know Du Zhaohui

16:09.960 --> 16:11.720
came to Shengcheng a few years ago.

16:11.720 --> 16:12.750
It may seem like

16:13.320 --> 16:14.750
he's been doing decent business,

16:14.750 --> 16:15.440
but he can't possibly

16:15.440 --> 16:17.240
really cut ties with his family.

16:17.600 --> 16:19.150
And even if he's not part of it—

16:19.150 --> 16:19.960
don't forget—

16:20.790 --> 16:21.600
he's not the only son

16:21.600 --> 16:22.550
of the Du family.

16:24.270 --> 16:25.320
You mean,

16:25.840 --> 16:27.270
if Du Zhaohui

16:27.600 --> 16:29.270
gives us information

16:29.910 --> 16:31.750
and the Du family's interests gets harmed,

16:31.750 --> 16:32.670
Du Chengrong

16:33.360 --> 16:35.000
won't even spare his own son?

16:35.510 --> 16:36.720
Fathers and sons
turning against each other,

16:36.720 --> 16:37.720
brothers at odds—

16:38.120 --> 16:39.380
these are very common.

16:39.840 --> 16:40.750
But if Du Zhaohui

16:40.750 --> 16:41.440
really knows

16:41.440 --> 16:42.630
information about the smuggling case,

16:42.630 --> 16:43.120
then for you...

16:43.120 --> 16:43.650
Xiaolan,

16:50.270 --> 16:51.330
you've seen it too.

16:51.910 --> 16:53.640
This matter is very dangerous.

16:54.150 --> 16:54.870
After these two incidents,

16:54.870 --> 16:55.930
I'm even wondering

16:56.030 --> 16:56.620
whether I should

16:56.620 --> 16:58.120
continue investigating this.

16:58.120 --> 16:58.840
I fear

17:00.200 --> 17:01.930
I'd bringing danger to others.

17:03.000 --> 17:03.790
But can you really

17:03.790 --> 17:05.190
let go of Shi Kai's death?

17:06.880 --> 17:08.550
If you can't find the truth,

17:09.030 --> 17:10.760
will you really be able to stop?

17:11.480 --> 17:13.339
Then would you still be yourself?

17:13.720 --> 17:14.380
Zhou Cheng.

17:15.069 --> 17:16.270
Don't worry about me.

17:17.240 --> 17:18.480
I'll protect myself.

17:21.960 --> 17:22.550
Mr. Du.

17:23.550 --> 17:24.410
Are you willing

17:24.589 --> 17:26.050
to sell your house and car?

17:26.869 --> 17:28.600
She wants me to tighten my belt?

17:29.000 --> 17:30.460
I'd rather be a loan shark.

17:32.350 --> 17:33.510
Is that all you've got?

17:33.510 --> 17:35.710
No wonder Xia Xiaolan doesn't like you.

17:37.270 --> 17:38.730
Young Master, your phone.

17:42.030 --> 17:42.480
Hello?

17:44.480 --> 17:45.240
It's a deal.

17:45.720 --> 17:47.650
Don't forget what you promised me.

17:49.310 --> 17:50.440
If I do as you say,

17:50.750 --> 17:51.920
I'll have no way out.

17:52.790 --> 17:53.520
Don't worry.

17:53.750 --> 17:55.010
I'll make sure you win.

17:56.750 --> 17:57.160
Good.

17:57.790 --> 17:59.520
Then I'll make sure you win too.

18:02.030 --> 18:03.430
You'll definitely win,

18:03.680 --> 18:04.480
Young Master.

18:11.590 --> 18:12.540
Many records

18:13.000 --> 18:13.830
have become

18:13.830 --> 18:15.270
meaningless numbers.

18:15.880 --> 18:17.270
My memories are fading,

18:18.200 --> 18:19.260
and I'm fading too.

18:20.350 --> 18:21.610
I'm sorry, Zhou Cheng.

18:22.440 --> 18:24.500
I don't know how much time I have left.

18:25.440 --> 18:27.110
I just want the smuggling case

18:27.790 --> 18:29.000
and Xia Ziyu's matter

18:29.750 --> 18:30.950
to both come to an end.

18:34.310 --> 18:35.790
Young Master instructed

18:35.920 --> 18:37.440
that no one's allowed in.

18:38.070 --> 18:40.200
I'll let you know if he needs anything.

18:40.310 --> 18:41.110
Young Master.

18:41.350 --> 18:42.200
Where's Old Man?

18:42.200 --> 18:44.260
Master went to Nanyang for business.

18:44.960 --> 18:46.220
-You may leave.
-Okay.

18:46.920 --> 18:48.720
He went to Nanyang for business?

18:55.680 --> 18:57.480
Stepmother, you're so relaxed.

19:00.240 --> 19:02.350
These coffee beans are from South America.

19:02.350 --> 19:03.160
I wonder

19:03.880 --> 19:06.010
if they suit your taste, Young Master.

19:15.000 --> 19:15.730
Tastes good.

19:17.130 --> 19:18.090
But coffee

19:18.550 --> 19:20.210
is best drunk in a coffee shop.

19:20.550 --> 19:21.880
The beans don't matter.

19:22.370 --> 19:24.100
What matters is the atmosphere

19:24.510 --> 19:25.590
and the company.

19:28.180 --> 19:29.580
I heard a nice coffee shop

19:29.720 --> 19:31.520
recently opened in Shengcheng.

19:31.880 --> 19:33.280
Vivi, when you have time,

19:33.480 --> 19:35.210
ask Old Man to take you to try it.

19:38.270 --> 19:39.440
Young Master,

19:40.640 --> 19:41.970
what do you mean by that?

19:44.030 --> 19:44.960
Nothing really.

19:45.480 --> 19:46.310
Just

19:46.680 --> 19:48.410
telling you to go drink coffee.

19:48.960 --> 19:50.070
Don't worry.

19:50.590 --> 19:51.680
With Old Man there,

19:51.830 --> 19:52.960
even in Shengcheng,

19:53.200 --> 19:54.730
no one would dare touch you.

20:00.030 --> 20:02.090
Young Master, you're a smart person.

20:03.110 --> 20:04.160
In this family,

20:04.610 --> 20:05.160
you and I are supposed to

20:05.160 --> 20:06.440
support each other.

20:08.030 --> 20:09.350
Your relationship with Xia Xiaolan

20:09.350 --> 20:10.610
is none of my business.

20:10.960 --> 20:11.720
But

20:13.160 --> 20:14.830
if you dare ruin my plans,

20:15.640 --> 20:16.830
I'll make you pay.

20:22.720 --> 20:23.480
Since Xia Xiaolan

20:23.480 --> 20:25.000
agreed to work with you,

20:25.440 --> 20:26.880
Young Master, I believe you

20:26.880 --> 20:28.160
didn't tell her the full story

20:28.160 --> 20:29.240
about us.

20:30.830 --> 20:31.960
A word of advice:

20:32.470 --> 20:34.000
Xia Xiaolan holds grudges.

20:34.750 --> 20:36.070
If you lie to her,

20:36.880 --> 20:38.510
she'll make you pay tenfold.

20:41.880 --> 20:42.680
Young Master,

20:43.680 --> 20:45.010
watch out for yourself.

20:58.000 --> 20:59.030
We'll

20:59.030 --> 20:59.690
next month.

21:00.020 --> 21:00.880
Will you have enough time

21:00.880 --> 21:01.740
to buy the land?

21:03.480 --> 21:04.680
It's not like I can just buy the land

21:04.680 --> 21:05.610
whenever I want.

21:06.000 --> 21:08.110
Land in Shengcheng is really expensive.

21:08.110 --> 21:09.270
Only those in foreign trade

21:09.270 --> 21:10.720
can afford it right now.

21:11.110 --> 21:12.920
I still need to check the location.

21:12.920 --> 21:14.240
I can't afford a big plot,

21:14.240 --> 21:15.970
so I'll have to pick carefully.

21:17.680 --> 21:18.790
Anyway, if you need anything,

21:18.790 --> 21:19.720
just let me know.

21:21.880 --> 21:22.400
Look.

21:22.750 --> 21:23.880
According to Gangdao news,

21:23.880 --> 21:24.830
Du Zhaohui is selling

21:24.830 --> 21:26.210
his cars and houses.

21:26.240 --> 21:27.440
Is he going bankrupt?

21:29.880 --> 21:30.960
Really?

21:31.680 --> 21:32.740
That's great news.

21:32.880 --> 21:34.440
I even want to buy firecrackers

21:34.440 --> 21:35.440
to celebrate.

21:36.680 --> 21:37.590
Why are you reading

21:37.590 --> 21:38.920
Gangdao's newspapers?

21:39.110 --> 21:40.310
Well, Sis Bai said

21:40.490 --> 21:41.720
since we're close to Gangdao,

21:41.720 --> 21:42.350
we might do business there

21:42.350 --> 21:43.790
in the future.

21:44.240 --> 21:45.350
We should read more, learn more,

21:45.350 --> 21:47.150
and get more information first.

21:47.480 --> 21:48.750
Sis Bai is right.

21:48.920 --> 21:50.790
She thinks even more thoroughly
than I do now.

21:50.790 --> 21:52.510
We are still far behind you.

21:52.790 --> 21:53.960
When you have time,

21:54.070 --> 21:55.030
tell us more about

21:55.030 --> 21:56.240
house-building.

21:56.510 --> 21:57.960
Although we deal in
construction materials,

21:57.960 --> 21:59.400
it should be closely related

21:59.400 --> 22:00.680
to house-building.

22:00.960 --> 22:02.750
It's always better to know more,

22:02.750 --> 22:03.150
right?

22:03.480 --> 22:04.590
I want to listen too.

22:04.590 --> 22:05.550
Xiaolan,

22:05.550 --> 22:07.550
let me know when you start the class.

22:08.110 --> 22:09.880
Well, I'll charge tuition fees.

22:09.880 --> 22:11.110
No problem.

22:11.920 --> 22:13.550
I'm leaving now.

22:14.050 --> 22:14.960
Going to check on Cheng?

22:14.960 --> 22:15.400
Yes.

22:15.920 --> 22:17.040
Be safe on the road.

22:17.310 --> 22:18.040
Okay. Bye.

22:18.120 --> 22:18.650
Bye-bye.

22:23.200 --> 22:25.330
Why does Xiaolan look so preoccupied?

22:25.720 --> 22:27.200
You haven't seen Cheng.

22:27.200 --> 22:29.460
He looks even more worried than Xiaolan.

22:32.750 --> 22:33.410
Zhou Cheng.

22:33.750 --> 22:35.550
The doctor just said that Yan...

22:37.110 --> 22:37.720
Auntie,

22:38.000 --> 22:39.130
is something wrong?

22:41.680 --> 22:42.440
You didn't tell her

22:42.440 --> 22:43.440
what I said to you?

22:44.270 --> 22:44.830
Auntie,

22:45.200 --> 22:45.920
I've already told you

22:45.920 --> 22:47.000
it's impossible.

22:47.510 --> 22:48.790
There's no need to tell Xiaolan.

22:48.790 --> 22:50.050
What's your plan then?

22:50.240 --> 22:51.070
My daughter got injured

22:51.070 --> 22:52.200
while working on a case with you, right?

22:52.200 --> 22:53.440
You're discharged now,

22:53.440 --> 22:54.070
but what about her?

22:54.070 --> 22:55.000
She's so pitiful.

22:55.000 --> 22:55.440
The injuries on her arms

22:55.440 --> 22:56.970
and her back are so severe.

22:57.000 --> 22:59.960
It hurts so much every time
they change her dressings.

22:59.960 --> 23:00.550
Auntie,

23:01.350 --> 23:02.880
may I ask what this is about?

23:03.310 --> 23:04.160
-Alright, since he won't tell you,
-Xiaolan.

23:04.160 --> 23:04.720
I will.

23:04.740 --> 23:06.350
This has nothing to do with you.

23:06.350 --> 23:07.110
Don't ask about it.

23:07.110 --> 23:08.680
How can it have nothing to do with her?

23:08.680 --> 23:10.070
What do you mean?

23:10.640 --> 23:11.790
I'm telling you one more time—

23:11.790 --> 23:13.720
my daughter got seriously injured

23:13.720 --> 23:14.960
while working on a case with you.

23:14.960 --> 23:15.720
Her future—

23:15.800 --> 23:16.550
her whole life—

23:16.550 --> 23:17.960
you have to take responsibility for it.

23:17.960 --> 23:19.240
Auntie, I've told you

23:19.350 --> 23:20.950
I will take responsibility,

23:21.110 --> 23:22.040
but not in the way

23:23.070 --> 23:23.930
you suggested.

23:41.920 --> 23:42.980
Xiaolan, sit down.

23:43.050 --> 23:43.860
Let's talk.

23:51.240 --> 23:52.110
You want to talk about

23:52.110 --> 23:53.640
Jiang Yan's mother, right?

23:54.640 --> 23:56.200
She wants you to marry Jiang Yan?

23:56.200 --> 23:57.070
But I already told her

23:57.070 --> 23:58.200
that's impossible.

23:58.480 --> 24:00.070
I can help Jiang Yan find a doctor

24:00.070 --> 24:00.800
to treat her,

24:01.070 --> 24:01.830
but anything else

24:01.830 --> 24:03.090
is really impossible.

24:03.400 --> 24:05.270
Besides, we've long agreed on
the boundaries

24:05.270 --> 24:06.790
between helping someone
and showing gratitude,

24:06.790 --> 24:07.240
right?

24:07.750 --> 24:09.010
Why are you panicking?

24:09.160 --> 24:10.160
I'm not mad.

24:10.830 --> 24:11.720
I trust you.

24:12.960 --> 24:14.400
But it's not surprising

24:14.400 --> 24:15.680
that Jiang Yan's mother said that.

24:15.680 --> 24:17.410
After all, when she was little...

24:17.410 --> 24:18.000
That was

24:18.000 --> 24:19.460
when we were really young.

24:19.550 --> 24:21.510
Later, her family moved to Jinling,

24:21.510 --> 24:22.880
and we barely saw each other
after that.

24:22.880 --> 24:23.920
And Jiang Yan has long

24:23.920 --> 24:24.780
known about us.

24:24.790 --> 24:25.440
It's just her mother

24:25.440 --> 24:26.970
trying to play matchmaker.

24:27.440 --> 24:29.680
Her mother is probably just worried

24:29.680 --> 24:31.000
that this incident will affect

24:31.000 --> 24:32.130
Jiang Yan's future.

24:32.400 --> 24:34.310
After all, appearance

24:34.310 --> 24:35.970
is quite important for a girl.

24:38.880 --> 24:39.940
But no matter what,

24:40.350 --> 24:41.070
I will definitely

24:41.070 --> 24:42.270
make it clear to them.

24:42.550 --> 24:43.080
Xiaolan.

24:43.510 --> 24:44.240
Don't worry.

24:44.480 --> 24:45.720
I trust you.

24:46.880 --> 24:48.140
What I'm worried about

24:48.240 --> 24:49.310
is your safety.

24:51.440 --> 24:52.720
You escaped this time,

24:53.720 --> 24:55.320
but what if it happens again?

24:57.480 --> 24:58.480
But now that even Jiang Yan

24:58.480 --> 24:59.480
has been dragged into this,

24:59.480 --> 25:02.140
I absolutely cannot
give up the investigation.

25:05.640 --> 25:06.170
Alright.

25:06.790 --> 25:07.510
Let's not talk about this.

25:07.510 --> 25:08.200
I'm hungry.

25:08.750 --> 25:09.550
I'll go cook.

25:10.480 --> 25:11.480
Noodles with bean paste?

25:11.480 --> 25:11.880
Okay.

25:27.880 --> 25:29.440
I know you won't give up.

25:30.200 --> 25:31.310
I'm just worried—

25:31.920 --> 25:33.520
are you facing these dangers

25:33.550 --> 25:35.350
really only because of the case,

25:36.310 --> 25:37.070
or could it also have something to do

25:37.070 --> 25:38.270
with my presence?

25:39.400 --> 25:41.600
How much longer can I stay here with you?

25:42.440 --> 25:43.350
Should I get closer to you

25:43.350 --> 25:44.550
or stay away from you?

25:46.640 --> 25:48.040
I have so many questions,

25:48.240 --> 25:49.680
but I can't find the answers,

25:49.680 --> 25:51.410
and I can't bring myself to ask.

26:02.030 --> 26:02.690
Auntie Liu.

26:03.030 --> 26:04.680
Gong Yang, what brings you here?

26:04.680 --> 26:06.510
I'm here to get the blueprints
from Ms. Xia.

26:06.510 --> 26:07.880
Xiaolan isn't back yet.

26:09.610 --> 26:10.070
I'm back.

26:10.070 --> 26:10.670
Gong Yang.

26:11.330 --> 26:12.200
You want the blueprints, right?

26:12.200 --> 26:13.200
I totally forgot.

26:13.480 --> 26:14.840
You didn't come to the office
this afternoon.

26:14.840 --> 26:15.830
I just got off work,

26:15.830 --> 26:17.110
so I stopped by on my way.

26:17.110 --> 26:18.030
Mr. Mao said we must
have the blueprints ready

26:18.030 --> 26:19.030
at work tomorrow.

26:19.270 --> 26:19.550
Wait,

26:19.550 --> 26:20.810
why didn't you call me?

26:20.880 --> 26:22.740
I did, but I couldn't get through.

26:25.790 --> 26:26.790
The battery died.

26:26.970 --> 26:27.570
I'm sorry.

26:27.590 --> 26:28.400
I was just too busy this afternoon.

26:28.400 --> 26:28.880
Wait a moment here.

26:28.880 --> 26:29.640
I'll go upstairs and get them for you.

26:29.640 --> 26:30.030
Okay.

26:33.550 --> 26:35.680
She's been so scatterbrained lately.

26:35.720 --> 26:37.050
Ms. Xia is just too busy.

26:39.160 --> 26:40.640
Sorry for making you
come all this way today.

26:40.640 --> 26:42.240
I'll count this as overtime.

26:42.790 --> 26:44.520
Mr. Mao said he missed you a bit.

26:45.130 --> 26:45.780
I know.

26:45.880 --> 26:47.680
He just wants to scold me, right?

26:48.470 --> 26:49.350
We can still handle it.

26:49.350 --> 26:50.950
Ms. Xia, get some rest early.

26:53.400 --> 26:54.410
Get home safely.

26:54.550 --> 26:55.880
Sure thing, Ms. Xia. See you tomorrow.

26:55.880 --> 26:56.880
See you tomorrow.

27:20.110 --> 27:21.640
If things keep going like this,

27:21.640 --> 27:23.500
everything will fall into chaos,

27:24.070 --> 27:26.130
and they'll notice something's off.

27:27.030 --> 27:27.640
Xiaolan.

27:27.790 --> 27:29.390
Come have some chicken soup.

27:31.240 --> 27:31.700
Come on.

27:32.030 --> 27:33.430
Drink it while it's warm.

27:33.510 --> 27:34.270
Thanks, Mom.

27:36.270 --> 27:37.510
There's been so much going on lately.

27:37.510 --> 27:38.960
It's been tough, hasn't it?

27:38.960 --> 27:40.920
If you're tired, just have some rest.

27:40.920 --> 27:42.520
But I don't have time to rest.

27:44.550 --> 27:45.270
However, it's really about time

27:45.270 --> 27:46.440
I hire an assistant.

27:47.550 --> 27:48.000
Mom.

27:48.110 --> 27:50.170
How's You Li been performing lately?

27:50.310 --> 27:51.070
You Li?

27:52.980 --> 27:54.710
That girl is really quite good.

27:54.790 --> 27:56.830
She's hardworking and willing to learn.

27:56.830 --> 27:57.270
You know,

27:57.270 --> 27:58.350
she's been really fluent

27:58.350 --> 27:59.410
in English lately.

27:59.550 --> 28:00.640
She has no problem

28:00.640 --> 28:02.640
communicating with clients at all.

28:02.720 --> 28:04.720
Do you want her to be your assistant?

28:06.110 --> 28:07.370
I think that will work.

28:14.310 --> 28:14.830
You Li.

28:15.400 --> 28:16.930
Come here when you're done.

28:24.640 --> 28:25.310
Ms. Xia.

28:25.510 --> 28:26.370
Come, sit down.

28:29.550 --> 28:30.070
You Li,

28:30.480 --> 28:31.960
you've been with us
since the store opened.

28:31.960 --> 28:33.490
You're a veteran employee,

28:33.750 --> 28:35.640
and you've been performing very well.

28:35.640 --> 28:36.720
During training before,

28:36.720 --> 28:37.750
I told you all

28:38.240 --> 28:39.590
that as long as you perform well,

28:39.590 --> 28:41.850
there will be better job opportunities.

28:42.030 --> 28:42.920
So I wanted to

28:42.920 --> 28:44.200
ask for your opinion:

28:44.590 --> 28:46.790
would you be willing to be my assistant?

28:48.720 --> 28:49.830
So here's the thing.

28:49.830 --> 28:51.070
I'm about to start

28:51.100 --> 28:52.200
a real estate company—

28:52.200 --> 28:53.680
buying land and building houses.

28:53.680 --> 28:55.000
The design work

28:55.030 --> 28:55.920
of my uncle's projects

28:55.920 --> 28:56.550
will also be merged

28:56.550 --> 28:57.440
into my studio.

28:57.510 --> 28:58.570
So as my assistant,

28:58.680 --> 29:00.650
you'll need to not only
handle matters for Luna,

29:00.650 --> 29:01.970
but also take care of

29:02.000 --> 29:03.590
the real estate and design work.

29:03.590 --> 29:04.190
Oh, right—

29:04.250 --> 29:05.240
there's also a materials center.

29:05.240 --> 29:06.030
But there isn't much work

29:06.030 --> 29:06.720
over there.

29:06.720 --> 29:08.720
You just need to go there occasionally.

29:08.720 --> 29:09.480
Ms. Xia,

29:10.110 --> 29:11.240
with so much work,

29:11.720 --> 29:13.320
I'm afraid I can't handle it.

29:14.680 --> 29:15.200
Yeah,

29:15.510 --> 29:16.790
I know it's not easy.

29:17.350 --> 29:19.580
I could put an ad in the paper
for a college student,

29:19.580 --> 29:20.540
but I think

29:20.770 --> 29:21.280
your ability

29:21.280 --> 29:22.590
is no worse than theirs,

29:22.590 --> 29:23.960
and you have more

29:23.960 --> 29:25.620
work experience than they do.

29:27.240 --> 29:28.070
How about this?

29:28.070 --> 29:29.480
You don't have to give me an answer
right away.

29:29.480 --> 29:30.940
Go back and think about it.

29:31.070 --> 29:32.240
As for the salary,

29:32.400 --> 29:33.600
-I think...
-Ms. Xia.

29:34.310 --> 29:36.110
Thank you for your recognition.

29:36.480 --> 29:37.480
But I'm afraid

29:37.550 --> 29:39.350
I still can't be your assistant.

29:39.590 --> 29:40.650
I'm sorry, Ms. Xia.

29:40.720 --> 29:42.180
I'm going back to work now.

29:42.310 --> 29:42.920
Thank you.

29:51.000 --> 29:51.720
You Li?

29:53.200 --> 29:54.530
She's quite motivated,

29:54.590 --> 29:55.720
and she loves to learn.

29:55.720 --> 29:56.350
Why would she turn down

29:56.350 --> 29:57.640
such a good opportunity?

29:57.640 --> 29:58.270
Exactly.

29:58.440 --> 30:00.030
At first,

30:00.030 --> 30:01.510
she seemed quite interested.

30:01.510 --> 30:03.040
But later, I don't know why,

30:03.400 --> 30:04.350
without even considering it,

30:04.350 --> 30:05.070
she just stood up,

30:05.070 --> 30:06.000
bowed and left.

30:06.880 --> 30:08.510
Could it be that the workload's so heavy

30:08.510 --> 30:09.590
that she got scared away?

30:09.590 --> 30:11.030
The workload is indeed heavy,

30:11.030 --> 30:12.430
but I couldn't lie to her.

30:12.800 --> 30:14.210
But I also told her

30:14.240 --> 30:15.000
it's mainly about

30:15.000 --> 30:16.260
the work at the studio.

30:16.350 --> 30:17.270
There won't be much work

30:17.270 --> 30:19.130
at Happy Life Materials and Luna.

30:20.800 --> 30:23.200
Whoever started the trouble should end it.

30:23.440 --> 30:24.440
I'd better step in

30:24.680 --> 30:25.940
to handle this matter.

30:26.310 --> 30:27.030
Why?

30:27.510 --> 30:28.590
What does it have to do with you?

30:28.590 --> 30:29.440
I guess

30:29.550 --> 30:30.720
You Li

30:30.720 --> 30:31.550
is just self-conscious.

30:31.550 --> 30:32.720
It must be because of that incident

30:32.720 --> 30:34.980
that she feels too embarrassed to see me.

30:36.070 --> 30:36.680
Wei.

30:37.160 --> 30:37.720
That incident

30:37.720 --> 30:39.070
happened ages ago.

30:39.240 --> 30:40.480
I'm afraid little You Li

30:40.480 --> 30:42.410
doesn't even remember who you are.

30:43.350 --> 30:44.750
I think Zhenzhu is right.

30:45.550 --> 30:47.550
You Li probably has other concerns.

30:48.000 --> 30:48.830
What concerns?

30:48.830 --> 30:49.640
She's just a young girl.

30:49.640 --> 30:50.750
What concerns could she possibly have?

30:50.750 --> 30:52.750
I'm the only possible concern here.

30:52.750 --> 30:53.680
Yeah, right. You're her concern.

30:53.680 --> 30:54.340
Yes, right.

30:54.440 --> 30:55.310
Leave this to me.

30:55.310 --> 30:56.270
You definitely are.

30:56.270 --> 30:56.790
San!

30:57.240 --> 30:58.310
We'd like to order more.

30:58.310 --> 30:58.840
Alright.

30:59.590 --> 31:00.920
Sis Bai, this one dish isn't enough.

31:00.920 --> 31:01.680
Think about it. What other dishes
do you want?

31:01.680 --> 31:02.480
What other dishes do you want?

31:02.480 --> 31:03.410
Look at the menu.

31:04.350 --> 31:05.640
That matter you asked me to check
last time—

31:05.640 --> 31:07.030
I've asked a friend
who does business in Nanyang

31:07.030 --> 31:07.760
look into it.

31:08.070 --> 31:09.010
How about shredded potatoes?

31:09.010 --> 31:10.110
Let's have shredded potatoes then.

31:10.110 --> 31:10.550
Sure.

31:11.640 --> 31:12.400
Thanks, San.

31:12.480 --> 31:13.140
No problem.

31:35.720 --> 31:36.780
Don't you feel hot?

31:37.350 --> 31:38.810
I'm used to the heat by now.

31:38.920 --> 31:40.850
Still investigating that worker?

31:43.150 --> 31:45.010
We've got news about that worker.

31:45.240 --> 31:45.970
We found him,

31:46.440 --> 31:47.700
but he died in Nanyang.

31:48.270 --> 31:49.730
I suspect he was murdered.

31:51.000 --> 31:51.880
This matter

31:52.110 --> 31:54.240
is getting more and more complicated.

31:55.200 --> 31:56.000
Will Jiang Yan

31:56.200 --> 31:57.780
still be involved in the case
going forward?

31:57.780 --> 31:59.030
You know Jiang Yan.

31:59.440 --> 32:00.440
After what happened,

32:00.440 --> 32:02.370
she'll definitely see it through.

32:02.380 --> 32:03.240
She also wants to see

32:03.240 --> 32:04.640
who's so bold as to

32:05.200 --> 32:06.590
target even lawyers

32:06.590 --> 32:07.590
and prosecutors.

32:08.000 --> 32:09.680
According to police leads,

32:10.110 --> 32:10.680
it's likely related

32:10.680 --> 32:11.810
to a smuggling ring.

32:12.920 --> 32:15.250
So Jiang Yan will definitely be involved.

32:16.480 --> 32:17.110
Cheng,

32:17.590 --> 32:18.550
aren't you worried

32:18.550 --> 32:19.810
Xiaolan will be upset?

32:22.240 --> 32:23.160
Xiaolan won't get upset

32:23.160 --> 32:24.620
over something like this.

32:25.110 --> 32:25.920
However...

32:26.480 --> 32:27.110
Look.

32:27.480 --> 32:27.960
Look.

32:28.270 --> 32:29.000
I knew it.

32:29.030 --> 32:30.310
It surely wasn't because

32:30.310 --> 32:31.110
you and Xiaolan were busy with work

32:31.110 --> 32:32.430
that you two didn't get married.

32:32.430 --> 32:33.760
Xiaolan is indeed busy,

32:34.720 --> 32:35.590
but I do have

32:36.210 --> 32:37.640
other concerns as well.

32:38.750 --> 32:41.210
You're worried this matter
will affect her?

32:43.310 --> 32:44.030
Look at you.

32:44.510 --> 32:46.270
What's wrong with you, Cheng?

32:46.730 --> 32:48.660
You're worrying about the future.

32:48.680 --> 32:49.650
You know what this is called?

32:49.650 --> 32:50.680
Borrowing trouble.

32:50.680 --> 32:52.000
Worrying for nothing.

32:52.350 --> 32:53.950
Why should you worry about Xiaolan?

32:53.950 --> 32:55.040
She's so smart.

32:55.070 --> 32:55.880
Even if problems come up in the future,

32:55.880 --> 32:57.610
you two can face them together.

32:57.680 --> 32:58.310
Look at you.

32:58.310 --> 32:59.480
You're usually smart.

32:59.480 --> 33:01.010
Why are you being silly now?

33:01.010 --> 33:02.350
I think you traded your IQ

33:02.350 --> 33:03.400
for love.

33:06.070 --> 33:07.200
Maybe you're right.

33:08.640 --> 33:10.040
But when you like someone

33:10.440 --> 33:11.570
and care about them,

33:11.830 --> 33:13.030
this is only natural.

33:13.550 --> 33:14.310
Once you have someone to care about,

33:14.310 --> 33:15.440
you'll understand.

33:16.030 --> 33:16.640
Forget it.

33:16.960 --> 33:17.830
It's too much trouble.

33:17.830 --> 33:18.960
I don't want to know.

33:19.110 --> 33:20.570
I'm going to take a shower.

33:36.110 --> 33:36.640
I'm here.

33:37.510 --> 33:39.240
Here's the hamburger I bought.

33:39.880 --> 33:40.590
In here.

33:41.350 --> 33:42.010
Here you go.

33:42.710 --> 33:44.120
This place opened last year.

33:44.120 --> 33:46.350
I've wanted to come,
but never had the time.

33:46.350 --> 33:47.830
I didn't expect there to be
so many people inside.

33:47.830 --> 33:49.030
T-There were no seats left.

33:49.030 --> 33:50.690
Sorry to make you eat outside.

33:51.480 --> 33:52.110
It's okay.

33:52.590 --> 33:53.790
It's quite nice here.

33:53.790 --> 33:55.050
The breeze feels nice.

33:57.320 --> 33:58.710
Come on, eat. It's tasty.

33:58.710 --> 33:59.150
Try it.

34:05.030 --> 34:05.640
How is it?

34:07.790 --> 34:09.670
It tastes a bit strange,

34:10.440 --> 34:12.170
but it's actually pretty good.

34:12.510 --> 34:14.969
It's different from
the food we usually eat.

34:16.550 --> 34:17.920
Well, our food is still better.

34:17.920 --> 34:19.510
How about we go to my friend's restaurant

34:19.510 --> 34:20.880
and order some stir-fried dishes?

34:20.880 --> 34:21.530
No need, really.

34:21.530 --> 34:22.380
This is fine.

34:23.630 --> 34:24.070
Okay.

34:29.960 --> 34:30.630
Mr. Kang.

34:32.110 --> 34:32.960
Actually,

34:33.400 --> 34:35.929
I should have apologized to you
a long time ago.

34:35.929 --> 34:37.000
Back at the hospital,

34:37.000 --> 34:38.280
I was too hasty.

34:40.639 --> 34:41.639
A-Actually,

34:41.670 --> 34:43.550
I've also wanted to ask you—

34:44.030 --> 34:44.840
what exactly happened

34:44.840 --> 34:45.840
back then?

34:47.030 --> 34:47.440
I...

34:49.710 --> 34:50.760
They all say...

34:51.190 --> 34:52.670
T-That you only liked me

34:52.670 --> 34:53.800
because you misjudged me,

34:53.800 --> 34:55.860
and once you realized, you dumped me.

34:56.670 --> 34:57.930
Don't choke. Careful.

35:03.960 --> 35:04.880
Actually,

35:06.000 --> 35:08.330
it was because
my mom was sick at that time,

35:08.800 --> 35:10.260
and I really needed money.

35:11.280 --> 35:12.280
Freshly steamed.

35:12.800 --> 35:13.400
Want some?

35:14.030 --> 35:14.670
Ma'am,

35:15.000 --> 35:16.360
how much for one?

35:16.550 --> 35:17.080
One dime.

35:19.630 --> 35:20.320
Want some?

35:25.630 --> 35:26.630
No thanks, Ma'am.

35:26.670 --> 35:27.400
I'm good.

35:28.710 --> 35:29.300
Thank you.

35:29.300 --> 35:29.830
Alright.

35:42.460 --> 35:43.000
Auntie?

35:43.110 --> 35:43.730
Uncle?

35:44.280 --> 35:45.210
Why are you here?

35:45.550 --> 35:46.360
Something this serious has happened.

35:46.360 --> 35:47.550
How could we not come?

35:47.550 --> 35:49.070
Luckily, we caught the last flight.

35:49.070 --> 35:49.590
Yeah.

35:49.760 --> 35:51.090
How's Wei doing, Cheng?

35:51.630 --> 35:52.610
I'm not sure either.

35:52.610 --> 35:53.670
Let's talk inside.

35:54.800 --> 35:55.460
Look at you.

35:56.710 --> 35:57.570
Let me tell you.

35:58.000 --> 35:59.130
This is Shengcheng.

36:00.440 --> 36:02.170
Since you did something wrong,

36:02.550 --> 36:04.410
you have to take responsibility!

36:05.230 --> 36:06.150
I could tell

36:06.550 --> 36:07.360
that your family

36:07.360 --> 36:08.490
was quite well-off,

36:09.170 --> 36:11.360
because you didn't even take
Gangdao merchants seriously.

36:11.360 --> 36:12.110
So I tried

36:13.400 --> 36:14.460
to get close to you,

36:15.230 --> 36:17.550
thinking if you and your mom liked me,

36:19.320 --> 36:21.050
perhaps I could get some money.

36:24.470 --> 36:25.020
Mr. Kang.

36:25.400 --> 36:26.400
I'm really sorry.

36:26.480 --> 36:27.680
It's okay. No need...

36:28.160 --> 36:28.840
-It's okay. It's okay.
-I… I...

36:28.840 --> 36:29.440
It's okay.

36:29.590 --> 36:30.670
There are so many people here.

36:30.670 --> 36:31.320
Come on, sit.

36:31.320 --> 36:32.070
Come on.

36:32.230 --> 36:33.150
Really, it's okay.

36:33.150 --> 36:33.750
It's okay.

36:34.400 --> 36:34.880
Well...

36:35.960 --> 36:37.090
What happened then?

36:37.190 --> 36:39.000
Y-You were scared off by Sis Bai?

36:41.190 --> 36:41.840
Kind of.

36:43.070 --> 36:43.960
And

36:44.400 --> 36:46.150
I had felt terrible about it all along.

36:46.150 --> 36:47.290
I knew it was wrong.

36:47.960 --> 36:49.110
I did need money,

36:49.650 --> 36:51.380
but my mom had always taught me

36:51.510 --> 36:52.630
to be upright

36:52.630 --> 36:54.090
and make an honest living.

36:54.620 --> 36:55.350
Later,

36:55.440 --> 36:57.190
I saw a job ad for Luna.

36:57.920 --> 36:59.650
It said no degree was required,

36:59.920 --> 37:02.150
as long as you're hardworking and capable.

37:02.150 --> 37:03.110
So I gave it a try.

37:04.110 --> 37:04.560
See?

37:04.590 --> 37:05.710
Isn't that great?

37:06.110 --> 37:07.360
Since we've talked

37:07.360 --> 37:08.290
everything out,

37:08.630 --> 37:10.030
don't feel burdened.

37:10.240 --> 37:11.450
And don't let this

37:11.480 --> 37:12.880
stop you from working for Xiaolan.

37:12.880 --> 37:14.320
It's such a good opportunity.

37:14.320 --> 37:15.030
From now on, we can also

37:15.030 --> 37:17.160
meet openly and without awkwardness.

37:17.230 --> 37:17.960
Mr. Kang.

37:19.230 --> 37:20.560
You've misunderstood.

37:20.630 --> 37:22.550
It wasn't because of that.

37:23.920 --> 37:25.110
Then what is it?

37:25.800 --> 37:26.710
Working for Xiaolan

37:26.710 --> 37:27.670
is a great opportunity.

37:27.670 --> 37:28.840
Don't be silly.

37:30.030 --> 37:30.480
I...

37:31.710 --> 37:33.630
I-I can't be Ms. Xia's assistant.

37:43.640 --> 37:44.510
Just pull over here.

37:44.510 --> 37:46.710
The road ahead is too narrow for the car.

37:51.150 --> 37:52.410
Well, be careful then.

37:56.590 --> 37:57.110
You.

37:58.030 --> 38:00.000
About Xiaolan's offer

38:00.000 --> 38:01.530
for you to be her assistant,

38:01.550 --> 38:02.750
give it more thought.

38:03.240 --> 38:04.080
I think it's a

38:04.110 --> 38:05.570
really good opportunity.

38:06.070 --> 38:07.710
And the fact that Xiaolan wants you

38:07.710 --> 38:09.670
proves she thinks you're capable enough.

38:09.670 --> 38:11.400
You can be a bit more confident.

38:19.260 --> 38:20.390
Let me help you down.

38:26.110 --> 38:27.400
Here. Careful.

38:29.800 --> 38:30.400
Thank you.

38:30.510 --> 38:31.150
No problem.

38:31.150 --> 38:31.960
Be careful.

38:32.190 --> 38:32.630
Okay.

38:32.750 --> 38:33.660
I'll go in now.

39:10.400 --> 39:12.200
She seems like she wants to do it.

39:13.000 --> 39:14.530
Why does she keep refusing?

39:20.710 --> 39:21.190
Mom.

39:21.760 --> 39:22.590
I'm back.

39:25.550 --> 39:26.070
Dad?

39:26.930 --> 39:28.190
You... You're home?

39:29.070 --> 39:31.270
I thought you had the night shift today.

39:32.960 --> 39:34.560
You've been drinking again.

39:39.070 --> 39:40.480
So what if I drank?

39:41.360 --> 39:42.400
You little bitch.

39:43.920 --> 39:45.980
You really are my good daughter, huh?

39:46.700 --> 39:48.100
Think you're all grown up

39:48.590 --> 39:49.990
and want to run away, huh?

39:51.880 --> 39:53.550
I knew something was

39:53.550 --> 39:54.590
off lately.

39:55.110 --> 39:57.020
You thought you could hide this from me?

39:57.020 --> 39:58.940
Your mother told me everything!

39:59.230 --> 40:00.290
Trying to run away?

40:00.880 --> 40:01.360
No...

40:02.250 --> 40:04.000
You want to go off on your own
and live the good life?

40:04.000 --> 40:04.590
No...

40:04.840 --> 40:06.100
I'll beat you to death!

40:06.400 --> 40:07.190
You!

40:07.440 --> 40:09.960
I'll kill you and your mother,

40:10.110 --> 40:12.230
so you give up on that idea!

40:13.070 --> 40:13.800
Get in there!

40:17.030 --> 40:17.590
Mom!

40:18.280 --> 40:18.840
Mom!

40:19.030 --> 40:20.590
Mom, what's wrong? Mom!

40:21.090 --> 40:22.250
Run... Run...

40:22.280 --> 40:23.000
Scream!

40:23.510 --> 40:24.960
Scream louder!

40:25.320 --> 40:26.960
Call all the neighbors over

40:27.280 --> 40:29.170
and let them see your mother naked!

40:29.170 --> 40:30.820
Mom! Don't! Mom!

40:31.670 --> 40:32.510
Don't! Mom!

40:32.920 --> 40:33.630
Don't! Mom!

40:33.630 --> 40:34.960
That sounds like You Li.

40:35.400 --> 40:36.030
Bastard!

40:36.190 --> 40:37.650
It really sounds like her.

40:37.880 --> 40:38.550
She's my mother!

40:38.550 --> 40:39.920
She's also your wife!

40:40.030 --> 40:40.630
You beast!

40:40.710 --> 40:41.710
I'm a beast?

40:42.280 --> 40:43.280
Then what are you?

40:43.590 --> 40:44.940
You're not my own flesh and blood.

40:44.940 --> 40:46.950
No matter how I raise you, it's useless!

40:46.950 --> 40:49.010
I'd be better off raising a dog!

40:49.400 --> 40:50.150
I'll

40:50.510 --> 40:52.230
break your legs right now!

40:55.320 --> 40:57.710
I'm going to tell the police right now!

40:57.920 --> 40:59.480
I'm going to tell the subdistrict office!

40:59.480 --> 40:59.880
You...

41:02.030 --> 41:02.840
Run then!

41:03.280 --> 41:05.210
Run and I'll beat your mom to death!

41:07.880 --> 41:08.940
What are you doing?

41:09.630 --> 41:10.480
Let go!

41:12.970 --> 41:13.960
What are you doing?

41:13.960 --> 41:15.480
I'll fight you to the death!

41:15.480 --> 41:17.280
I'll fight you to the death! I...

41:19.880 --> 41:21.410
I'll fight you to the death!

41:24.400 --> 41:26.320
Come any closer and I'll kill you!

41:26.670 --> 41:27.510
Kill me?

41:28.230 --> 41:30.090
Do you even know how to use a knife?

41:31.030 --> 41:31.960
I'll kill you!

41:34.150 --> 41:35.150
Kill me then!

42:03.070 --> 42:03.650
What happened?

42:03.650 --> 42:04.780
Did a thief break in?

42:04.840 --> 42:05.710
I'm here. Don't be afraid.

42:05.710 --> 42:07.040
What happened? Tell me!

42:07.510 --> 42:08.030
He...

42:08.320 --> 42:09.760
He killed my mom.

42:10.070 --> 42:10.730
Your mom...

42:19.150 --> 42:19.590
You Li!

42:19.920 --> 42:21.110
Your mom's still alive.

42:21.110 --> 42:21.880
Mom!

42:23.190 --> 42:23.800
Mom!

42:24.880 --> 42:25.400
Mom.

42:26.190 --> 42:26.840
Kang Wei.

42:27.280 --> 42:28.000
Save my mom.

42:28.280 --> 42:29.110
I'm begging you!

42:29.110 --> 42:30.840
I'll do anything to repay you!

42:31.670 --> 42:32.320
You Li.

42:32.510 --> 42:33.840
Stop talking nonsense.

42:33.840 --> 42:34.880
Get your mom and that guy

42:34.880 --> 42:35.730
into my car.

42:35.760 --> 42:37.490
I'll take them to the hospital.

42:37.960 --> 42:39.550
Why save that beast?

42:40.110 --> 42:41.000
Don't be stupid.

42:41.000 --> 42:42.600
Leaving him to die is murder!

42:42.610 --> 42:43.190
What could be

42:43.190 --> 42:44.150
more important than yourself?
